creator: Eurosoft Tech Limited
descriptionHtml:
CabTreasure Driver App operates with Cab Treasure Dispatch System. Drivers who are registered with the company who is using CabTreasure Booking & Dispatch system can start using the app by submitting Authorization (Activation) Code.

CabTreasure Driver App is designed and developed to increase the efficiency of booking management and security of passengers by providing the accurate geo location of driver and better communication service.

CabTreasure Driver App allows driver to receive and manage booking along with below features

Communicate with operator via built-in chat service
View Job History
View Available and Queue (Follow-on) Bookings
Manage Allocated Future Bookings
Fare calculator and fixed pricing

Integrated with variant of card payment providers.



Contact us get detailed information on Cab Treasure Booking & Dispatch System.
